All in all i would stay there again but would request having a fridge as all of the rooms do not have them and the ice machine played up alot.	The manager on duty was unfriendly and didn't even offer help, until he finally called the police.	Once we arrived, the staff was friendly and welcoming with a guest service stand willing to help.	Also the guys at the front desk were helpful, and the park tickets and advice given were of great help (for my wallet as well).